## 5. Deletion procedures

- Soft-delete on user request or account closure, hard-delete after
  the period above.
- Backups containing Personal Data are rotated such that user data is
  fully removed from backup media within the retention period plus
  backup-rotation interval.
- Anonymised aggregates may be retained for analytics indefinitely.

## 6. Exceptions

Data subject to a legal hold, regulatory obligation, or active
investigation is retained until the obligation is discharged.
[LEGAL REVIEW REQUIRED] — list applicable retention obligations
(tax, AML/KYC, employment, etc.).

## 7. Review cadence

This policy is reviewed at least annually and whenever data categories
change.

